'Hello there! It's about time! I've been waiting for service for quite a long while, and this order isn't filling itself, you know.\n\n'Here is my list. Please find these items at once! I haven't got all day.'

Items from the market list can be found throughout Bywater during the Farmers Faire. The market list is in your inventory.\n\nYou should collect the items on the market list...but avoid collecting items that are not listed.
'Oh, well done, [placeholder]! Filling these orders can be tricky, but I see that you got everything to make this patron happy.\n\nYou are a great help!'
Daisy Sandyman is at the market stall at the Farmers Faire.\n\nYou should bring the goods you collected to Daisy Sandyman.
